00:33:19,300 --> 00:33:20,200
Scott: It's a good game to have.

691
00:33:20,320 --> 00:33:28,450
Scott: If you know, if you want to whip something out really quickly and you're a very wordy kind of, you know, linguistic, lingual file kind of person, you know, Boggle is a good one.

